  "title": "Project Executive $4.5K #EAA",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Manage and handle lighting projects.</p></li><li><p>Attend meetings with Clients, Developers, Architects, Lighting Consultants and Main Contractors.</p></li><li><p>Prepare technical reports and installation diagrams.</p></li><li><p>Schedule and handle work order preparations.</p></li><li><p>Supervise installation works at project sites.</p></li><li><p>Liaise with Main Contractors and Sub Contractors.</p></li><li><p>Handle testing of LEDs and lighting projects.</p></li><li><p>Prepare and submit operational and maintenance reports.</p></li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>NITEC/Diploma in Electrical Engineering</p></li><li><p>3 to 5 years of project management experience in the lighting or construction industry.</p></li><li><p>Proficient in AutoCad.</p></li><li><p>Good communication skills.</p></li><li><p>Ability to multi task and work under tight deadlines.</p></li></ul><p><br />Aaron Teo Yiau Bing (CEI No. R1103712)<br />Contact Number: <a href=\"tel:6786 0100\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>6786 0100</strong></a><br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd<br />EA Licence No. 99C4599</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>",
